hema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[[{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How do I start a free trial of Photoshop?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"\n        \n          Click the Free Trial button.\n          Sign in or set up your Adobe ID and download your free trial.\n          After your 7-day free trial ends, your Creative Cloud membership will continue, unless canceled before free trial ends.\n        \n      ","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Is there a free version of Photoshop?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes, you can download a 7-day free trial of Photoshop on your computer. The free trial is the full version of the app and includes access to all the features and updates in the latest version of Photoshop including access to Photoshop on the web. Your free trial will automatically convert to a paid Creative Cloud subscription after 7 days, unless you cancel before then.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How can I cancel the Photoshop free trial?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"To cancel your Photoshop free trial, navigate to your Adobe account page within 7 days of starting the trial. Locate your plan name and click Manage Plans. Then click Cancel Plan. Indicate your cancellation reason, and then click continue. Follow the onscreen instructions to finish your cancellation. Get step-by-step cancellation instructions.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How can I get Photoshop for free?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"New customers can start a 7-day free trial of Photoshop anytime, which includes the desktop, web, iPhone, and iPad apps. To start a 7-day free trial of Photoshop:","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Is Photoshop free for students?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"No, Photoshop is not free for students, but students are eligible for a 7-day free trial and a discount of over 71% on Photoshop as part of the Creative Cloud Pro plan. Learn more about student plans.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How long does the free trial of Photoshop last?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Your free trial of Photoshop starts when you check out and lasts for seven days. The Photoshop trial will automatically convert to a paid Creative Cloud membership after 7 days, unless you cancel before then.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How can I extend the free trial of Photoshop?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Only one 7-day free trial of Photoshop is available per person. After your free trial ends, it will automatically convert to a paid Creative Cloud membership plan, unless you cancel before then. For free photo editing software and creative apps, check out Adobe Express.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Are the AI editing features in Photoshop free to use?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The Photoshop desktop app is not free, but you can sign up for a free trial and try the full version of the app, including all generative AI photo editing features like Generative Fill and Generative Expand, for 7 days. Or try editing images with the free version of the Adobe Firefly web app.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      What are the steps to install the Photoshop (beta) app with new generative AI features?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Get detailed instructions on steps to install the Photoshop (beta) app with new generative AI features.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Is there a free mobile version of Photoshop?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Photoshop mobile is free on iPhone and Android. You can also use Photoshop on the iPad for free. Add and remove objects, make targeted adjustments, collage and blend images, and more — all on your phone. To download, visit App store or Google play store.","@type":"Answer"}}]]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/global-navigation/utilities/menu/menu.css"><link rel="p